x":3,"text":"潮汐是地球与月球引力相互拉扯，导致潮涨潮落的一个过程，一般初一及十五前后最佳，有大潮汛🌊。潮间带的软体动物行动比较缓慢，没来得及返回大海🌊，留在🦆滩涂。人类及鸟类借助这个契机进行抓捕的行为，成为赶海🔮。\n五月进入禁止🚫出海捕鱼🔥还有最后两场\n出海捕鱼🐟的机会，错过了就要在等3️⃣个月\n深圳居然有超多海货😍的亲子赶海圣地，可以体验游艇🛳出海捕鱼🐠的乐趣哦。\n‼️如何报名❓评论区留言📩，我来联系您📸\n\t\n#周末去哪儿 #Nature魔法教室  #深圳亲子游  #深圳遛娃好去处  #深圳遛娃  #赶海  #深圳赶海#深圳亲子#深圳周末去哪儿 #深圳周末亲子游 #户外赶海 #户外赶海抓海鲜 #遛娃 #深圳海岛 #深圳研学 #本地人去哪玩 #深圳假期遛娃 #五一深圳怎么玩#赶海图鉴 ","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/chg","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 998, 1023)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 1865 - 1039, 2400)"},{"index":4,"text":"04-19 广东","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eil","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 998, 35)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 2930 - 1039, 2400)"},{"index":5,"text":"共 41条评论","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eh1","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 189, 55)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 3062 - 230, 2400)"},{"index":6,"resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/bx","class":"android.widget.RelativeLayout","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 143)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 3117 - 1080, 2400)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"爱评论的人运气都不差~","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eh2","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.